org.impact2585.lib2585

Class Drivetrain

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.impact2585.lib2585.Drivetrain
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Destroyable

    public class Drivetrain
extends java.lang.Object
implements Destroyable
    This class contains drivetrain code for the robot WPILib will square rotation by default, but this class will use the same rotation exponent as specified If you want your drivetrain to have the same behavior as in WPILib, pass in 2 as the primary rotation exponent
